which is <normalised orig="vsuall" auto="true">usual</normalised>, and common, cannot properly<lb/>
be called a miracle. A miracle <normalised orig="therfore" auto="true">therefore</normalised><lb/>
must be a rare <normalised orig="worke" auto="true">work</normalised> of God, <normalised orig="sildome" auto="true">seldom</normalised><lb/>
brought to <normalised orig="passe" auto="true">pass</normalised>, &amp; for this cause we cannot<lb/>
say, that repentance, or regeneration<lb/>
is a miracle, for although repentance <normalised orig="bee" auto="true">be</normalised><lb/>
