of nature, yet because they are not rare<lb/>
but <normalised orig="vsuall" auto="true">usual</normalised>, and ordinary, they be no miracles.<lb/>
An Adamant stone (wee know not by<lb/>
what force) will draw Iron to it <normalised orig="selfe" auto="true">self</normalised>:<lb/>
Iron is <normalised orig="heauy" auto="true">heavy</normalised> of it <normalised orig="selfe" auto="true">self</normalised>, and of it self cannot<lb/>
possibly <normalised orig="mooue" auto="true">move</normalised> from place to place,<lb/>
yet an Adamant if it <normalised orig="bee" auto="true">be</normalised> <normalised orig="aboue" auto="true">above</normalised> it will<lb/>
