<normalised orig="worke" auto="true">work</normalised> that <normalised orig="commeth" auto="true">comes</normalised> to <normalised orig="passe" auto="true">pass</normalised>, not ordinaly,<lb/>
but very <normalised orig="sildome" auto="true">seldom</normalised>.<lb/>
This <normalised orig="worke" auto="true">work</normalised> is called rare, either in regard<lb/>
of the thing wrought, or in regard of<lb/>
the manner of working it. First in respect<lb/>
