Apparently wrought, &amp;c.<lb/>
Thirdly, a miracle must <normalised orig="haue" auto="true">have</normalised> this annexed<lb/>
<normalised orig="vnto" auto="true">unto</normalised> it: for it must not be obscure,<lb/>
