So they saw most <normalised orig="euidently" auto="true">evidently</normalised> the walls<lb/>
of <normalised orig="Iericho" auto="true">Jericho</normalised> <normalised orig="fal" auto="true">fall</normalised> down: and therefore if there<lb/>
