<normalised orig="selfe" auto="true">self</normalised>, it is no miracle. Likewise what<lb/>
<normalised orig="workes" auto="true">works</normalised> so <normalised orig="euer" auto="true">ever</normalised> be done by satan or any of<lb/>
his Angels, if it be not <normalised orig="euident" auto="true">evident</normalised> &amp; to be discerned<lb/>
